    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>pine nuts</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until toasted</p><p>Once toasted, transfer them to a bowl and set aside for later</p>",
      "order": 2,
