    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve the <strong>sun-dried tomato paste </strong>and <strong>coconut yoghurt</strong> in 300ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [500ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your<strong> sun-dried tomato stock</strong></p>",
