          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a medium-high heat</p><p>Add the <strong>sun-dried tomato stock</strong>, <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong>, <strong>quick-cook amorini </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cook, covered, for an initial 2 min</p>",
