    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained cannellini beans</strong> and <strong>washed</strong> <strong>spinach</strong> to the pan and stir it all together</p><p>Cook, covered, for 3 min further or until the pasta is cooked through – this is your <strong>creamy sun-dried tomato pasta</strong></p>",
